tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE RiskProfiles (
  id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  applicant_name VARCHAR(50),
  age INT,
  gender VARCHAR(10),
  occupation VARCHAR(50),
  policy_type VARCHAR(20),
  risk_score DECIMAL(5,2)
);

CREATE TABLE historical_data (
    entry_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    applicant_id INT,
    age INT,
    gender VARCHAR(10),
    occupation VARCHAR(50)
);
